summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 10E & 11W, page 52 & 53, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1-7 incl. Block 7, Portions of Lots 8-10 incl. on north side of Harley Ave., Block 8, Portions of Lots 12-14 incl. on north side of Harley Ave., Block 12, all in Lawton Park Add. - and Portions of Section 10, Township 25, Range 3E and Section 11, Township 25, Range 3E, on the north side of Commodore Way.
